layout.text: With an emphasis on high-quality and diversity, Tamara is the ideal destination to find exquisite Decor & Accessories unlike any you might find. All items are hand- picked and include hand-crafted kitsch bags, fashion accessories, glassware, ceramics, art, stone and wooden sculptures, fountains, furnishings, hand painted panels and windows, frames, table tops, lamps and lots more….
